## American professional association

Not to be confused with the [Institution of Electrical Engineers](/Institution_of_Electrical_Engineers) (IEE), which, despite a similar acronym, is an entirely separate entity based in the UK, or [Industrial Electronic Engineers](/Industrial_Electronic_Engineers) (IEE), because apparently, clarity is optional in naming conventions.

